casebody.data:
Wednesday, October 30, 1991

MERIT DOCKET

91-2040. State, ex rel. Phillips, v. Lorain Cty. Bd. of Elections.

In Prohibition. This cause originated in this court on the filing of a complaint for a writ of prohibition.

IT IS ORDERED by the court, sua sponte, that this cause is hereby dismissed as moot, effective October 29, 1991.

Moyer, C.J., Sweeney, Holmes, Douglas, Wright, H. Brown and Resnick, JJ., concur.
